msgstr ""
"创建自定义的 ``layout.html`` Jinja2 模板，重载 ``fonts`` 块（示例用于加载包含在 ``_static/vendor`` 目录中的 Lato 字体）："

#: ../../user_guide/fonts.rst:50
msgid ""
"Your text may quickly show up as \"unstyled\" before the fonts are "
"loaded. To reduce this, you may wish to explore options for `preloading "
"content <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-"
"US/docs/Web/HTML/Preloading_content>`__, specifically the binary font "
"files. This ensures the files will be loaded before the CSS is parsed, "
"but should be used with care."
msgstr ""
"在字体加载之前，您的文本可能会很快显示为“未样式化”。为了减少这种情况，您可能需要探索 `预加载内容 <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Preloading_content>`__ "
"的选项，特别是二进制字体文件。这确保文件将在 CSS 解析之前加载，但应谨慎使用。"
